{
  "texts": [
    "In the real world, a fashionista can express their mood by the style and color of the clothing that they are wearing.",
    "For example, people in a good mood tend to wear brightly colored clothing.",
    "However, due to the limitations arising from the physical properties of the fabric, the color and style of clothing cannot be changed according to the mood of the wearer.",
    "In contrast, clothing in the Metaverse can overcome these limitations.",
    "The Metaverse allows designers to add variable properties to the clothing, such as images and colors, so that consumers can freely edit clothing elements based on their thoughts and emotions."
  ]
}